&gt; &gt; the stress on the &quot;ee&quot;. So I am 100% behind KR&#39;s rule of #26 for 
&gt; unstressed
&gt; &gt; terminal &quot;ily&quot; endings and the like.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; regards
